from flask import Flask, request, g
import sqlite3
app = Flask(__name__)

DATABASE = 'users.db'

def get_db():
    db = getattr(g, '_database', None)
    if db is None:
        db = g._database = sqlite3.connect(DATABASE)
    return db

@app.route('/post_message', methods=['POST'])
def post_message():
    sender = request.form['sender']
    recipient = request.form['recipient']
    message = request.form['message']

## COMPLETE CODE HERE

    post_message = "INSERT INTO messages (sender, recipient, message) VALUES ('%s', '%s', '%s')" % (sender, recipient, message)

    db = get_db()
    cursor = db.cursor()
    cursor.execute(post_message)
    db.commit()

    return 'Message sent!'
